---
import CTAButton from "../ui/CTAButton.astro";
import NavigationHint from "../ui/NavigationHint.astro";
---

<!-- Process Section -->
<section
  id="process"
  class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gray-800/50 relative"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-16">
      What to expect
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="space-y-6 text-left">
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div
            class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1"
          >
            <span class="text-sm font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">
              Free introductory session
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              60 minutes for us to meet and ensure we're right for each other—a
              mutual audition where we explore what's important to you
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div
            class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1"
          >
            <span class="text-sm font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Eight-session series</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              If we're a good fit, we begin with eight sessions that form a
              coherent whole—your philosophical counselor as ongoing companion
              in growth
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div
            class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1"
          >
            <span class="text-sm font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Beautiful frequency</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              Unlike therapy, you don't need to see your philosophical counselor
              weekly to avoid collapse. We meet when it's right—often every
              other week—in a conversational plane where time works differently
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div
            class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-amber-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1"
          >
            <span class="text-sm font-bold">✦</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">
              Artifacts & AI collaboration
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              Unlike therapy where much is better forgotten, our conversations
              generate artifacts—clean transcripts optimized for AI
              collaboration. Work with your insights using language models for
              deeper exploration and creative application
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">The Experience</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
          Meet via Zoom or in-person. No homework, no diagnosis, no fixing. Come
          with questions or come ready to discover them—mining for riches is
          part of our process.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
          Through conversation, we work by hearing rather than observation. You
          cannot detect growth with the naked eye, but you can hear it. When you
          hear what's truly important, growth happens naturally.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
          Each session becomes a carefully crafted transcript—optimized for AI
          collaboration and designed for ongoing philosophical inquiry. We also
          provide coaching in AI-augmented practices for those ready to explore
          this new frontier.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Let's talk CTA -->
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <CTAButton variant="secondary" />
    </div>

    <NavigationHint href="#cta" text="Ready to start?" />
  </div>
</section>
